modName: Elite Rogue Armour UNP-UNPB All-in-One Retexture
descriptionHtml:
Elite Rogue Armour UNP Retexture by anka01
Original Mod Author [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/users/6061662/?]KungFuMasterPS[/url]

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Hi,
this is my re-texture for the Elite Rogue Armour from [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/users/6061662/?]KungFuMasterPS[/url]

[heading]Update 1.20:[/heading]
Now the UNP/UNPB Version is available!
Endorse [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/users/6061662/?]KungFuMasterPS[/url] for his great work!

[heading]Update 1.10:[/heading]
all main outfits (longpants, hotpants, asymetricpants. innerwear, plates or only straps,
boots and jacket) are now craftable at forge in [b]black and darkbrown version[/b].
You don't need the orginal Mod!

If you [b]only[/b] want the darkbrown re-texture, you need the orginal Mod from here
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/30189//?

Hope you like it!

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Installation:

Install by dropping data folder into your skyrim folder!
(if you have the orginal Mod confirm overwriting!)

For only darkbrown re-texture download the orginal Mod,
then install mine retexture and confirm overwriting!

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Requirements:

The armor requires the
UNP body replacer http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6709
or Unpb body http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/20227
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Credits:

[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/users/6061662/?]KungFuMasterPS[/url] for this amazing Armor!!!
Thank you :)
